Last Broadcast Date: Thu 11 Aug 2011
Extraordinary personal stories from around the world. Today, the Armenian village deserted by its menfolk in their search for work. Also, how an American jogger punched an attacking bear and lived to tell the tale. And the former child refugee from Sudan who has just graduated from a top American university. Show less